    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those whose occupation or profession it is to engage in a game played indoors or out of doors with a large inflated ball, which is thrown from player to player, the object being to score by casting it into one's opponents' goal, a basket fixed ten feet above the ground at each end of the field of play.</Note_Text>
